  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK630">
<l>iṉṉāmai yiṉpa meṉakkoḷiṉākuntaṉ</l>
<l>ṉoṉṉār viḻaiyuñ ciṟappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The elevation, which even his enemies will esteem, will be gained by him, who regards pain as pleasure.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
